## 🚀 About

Welcome to my portfolio!  
Built from scratch with SwiftUI vibes, glitch animations, and backend power.

This site showcases my iOS + Full Stack projects including:
- 📺 Watchtime Analyzer (Node.js + SwiftUI app)
- 📈 Streaming JSON processing
- ⚡ Backend auto-deployment with GitHub Actions + Render

